data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This picture shows that a lot of tourists are on boats. They seem to be in Venice which is a very beautiful city because the buildings are built on water. These are European-style buildings. This reminds me of a trip to Venice when I was in high school. I was with my family. We had a good time. It was such a memorable experience that I can immediately recall when looking at this picture. I was also on a boat when touring the city. It's so much fun as you can never experience this in other places.
